pos_mean_info_list.mean: 案卷保管人；档案保管员

word_group.brief_definition: 视频存档；视频档案馆；视频档案
讨论组档案；讨论小组存档

bilingual.source: The original document is kept in the archive.
bilingual.target: 原始文件保存在档案馆里。

bilingual.source: The documents are stored in the archive room.
bilingual.target: 文件被储存的在档案室里。

bilingual.source: The lost documents were retrieved from the archive.
bilingual.target: 丢失的文件被从档案中取回。

bilingual.source: The company plans to digitalize its entire archive.
bilingual.target: 公司计划使数字化其整个档案。

bilingual.source: She created indexes for all the documents in the archive.
bilingual.target: 她为档案中的所有文件创建了索引。

bilingual.source: The archive contains rare photographs from the 19th century.
bilingual.target: 档案馆包含了19世纪的稀有照片。

bilingual.source: Researchers often visit the archive to gather information.
bilingual.target: 研究人员经常访问档案馆以收集信息。

bilingual.source: The company plans to digitize its entire archive of documents.
bilingual.target: 公司计划将其全部档案文件数字化。

bilingual.source: The library has an extensive archive of historical documents.
bilingual.target: 图书馆有一个广泛的历史文件档案馆。

bilingual.source: The librarian helped me retrieve the book from the archive.
bilingual.target: 图书管理员帮我从档案中取回了那本书。

list.abstract: Archive，文档服务器，Internet中的文档服务器，可定期自动地访问众多的InternetFTP服务器，将这些服务器上的文件索引成一个可以检索的数据库。

yingyinNormal.en: They are coming our way. London was not an archive. It was a top secret branch of Starfleet designated Section 31.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们正朝着我们前进呢。伦敦不只是个档案馆，还是星际舰队的一个高级机密分支，特指为31区。

yingyinNormal.en: World population, PC placements, the archive of all the medical literature, Moore's law, the old way of sequencing, and here's all the new stuff.
yingyinNormal.zh: 世界人口，PC配置，医学文献档案，摩尔定律，旧的测序方式，然后是这些新玩意。

yingyinNormal.en: Archive this configuration. Open up her primaries. Perception. Emotional acuity. Bump it. 1.5% Updating. Okay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 保存这个配置，打开她的基元认知能力，情感敏锐度提高百分之1.5。正在上传。好。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: the place where historical documents or records are kept

examination_example.sentence: "We realized in the mid-1970s that it was missing, " says Effie Kapsalis, head of the Smithsonian Institution <highlight>Archives</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 史密森学会档案馆负责人 Effie Kapsalis 说：“20世纪70年代中期我们就发现它丢失了。”

examination_example.sentence: A letter written by Charles Darwin in 1875 has been returned to the Smithsonian Institution <highlight>Archives</highlight> (档案馆) by the FBI after being stolen twice.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 查尔斯·达尔文(Charles Darwin)在1875年写的信在两次被盗后已被联邦调查局(FBI)退回史密森学会档案馆。

examination_example.sentence: The FBI worked closely with the <highlight>Archives</highlight> to determine that the letter was both authentic and definitely Smithsonian's property.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 联邦调查局(FBI)与档案馆密切合作，确定这封信既是真迹，而且绝对是史密森尼的财产。

sense_info_list.en: place or store something in an archive

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Archiving</highlight> practices have changed greatly since the 1970s.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 自20世纪70年代以来，归档做法发生了巨大变化。

sense_info_list.en: a collection of historical documents or records providing information about a place; institution; or group of people
